{"tid":2301782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葡籍歐洲議員兼高官去信中共外交部　要求探訪十二港人","createTime":"2020-11-26T14:33:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T15:01:53.000Z","uid":261647,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a11f1ba62492429232da535493ef0191239fb478","tid":2301782,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T14:33:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NathanLawKC/photos/a.645858435565493/2407643906053595/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNathanLawKC%2Fphotos%2Fa.645858435565493%2F2407643906053595%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=ME9RTGLMBg%2Fi%2BHfTLk0cjA9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=56864e0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NathanLawKC/photos/a.645858435565493/2407643906053595/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xTXb0st.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxTXb0st.jpg&h=feb3a505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者：羅冠聰 Nathan Law<br />\n <br />\n【🇪🇺歐洲戰線｜葡籍歐洲議員兼高官去信中共外交部 要求探訪十二港人】<br />\n<br />\n#save12hkyouths<br />\n<br />\n葡萄牙籍歐洲議員兼環境保護部部長Isabel Santos 近日表示，已經去信中共外交部及司法部，要求會見持有萄葡牙護照、現時被扣在留在深圳鹽田看守所12港人之一郭子麟，並促請求「歐盟外長」兼歐盟委員會副主席博雷爾（Josep Borrell）介入事件，捍衞葡萄牙公民的權利。<br />\n<br />\n她批評《國安法》相當險惡，北京日益利用這惡法，打壓香港爭取民主的街頭抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n每把聲音都很重要：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/isabel_mep/status/1331218218493628416\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fisabel_mep%2Fstatus%2F1331218218493628416&d=ME9RTGLMBg%2Fi%2BHfTLk0cjA9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=6c0e9db5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fisabel_mep%2Fstatus%2F1331218218493628416&h=c46cc53b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/isabel_mep/status/1331218218493628416</a>"},{"pid":"fdf5c76f878b0ce33b50911096a6ab3ec15f9aca","tid":2301782,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T14:34:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\"